{
  "page": "Kurz",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Kurz</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Kurz</b> is one of the criminals <a href=\"/index.php/Yoren\" title=\"Yoren\">Yoren</a> picked for the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%E2%80%99s_Watch\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Night’s Watch\">Night’s Watch</a> when he cleaned out the dungeons of <a href=\"/index.php/King%E2%80%99s_Landing\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"King’s Landing\">King’s Landing</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> and is part of the group marching north to the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kurz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Kurz had been arrested as a poacher.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kurz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kurz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Tarber_Cutjack_Kurz_Koss_and_Reysen_(ACoK_Comic).jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/00/Tarber_Cutjack_Kurz_Koss_and_Reysen_%28ACoK_Comic%29.jpg/350px-Tarber_Cutjack_Kurz_Koss_and_Reysen_%28ACoK_Comic%29.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"150\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/00/Tarber_Cutjack_Kurz_Koss_and_Reysen_%28ACoK_Comic%29.jpg/525px-Tarber_Cutjack_Kurz_Koss_and_Reysen_%28ACoK_Comic%29.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/00/Tarber_Cutjack_Kurz_Koss_and_Reysen_%28ACoK_Comic%29.jpg/700px-Tarber_Cutjack_Kurz_Koss_and_Reysen_%28ACoK_Comic%29.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Tarber_Cutjack_Kurz_Koss_and_Reysen_(ACoK_Comic).jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Tarber\" title=\"Tarber\">Tarber</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Cutjack\" title=\"Cutjack\">Cutjack</a>, Kurz, <a href=\"/index.php/Koss\" title=\"Koss\">Koss</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Reysen\" title=\"Reysen\">Reysen</a> resist the Gold Cloaks by Mel Rubi</div></div></div>\n<p>Moving north on the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsroad\" title=\"Kingsroad\">kingsroad</a>, the band arrives at an inn with a bathhouse where a group of <a href=\"/index.php/City_Watch_of_King%E2%80%99s_Landing\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"City Watch of King’s Landing\">gold cloaks</a> carrying an arrest warrant for <a href=\"/index.php/Gendry\" title=\"Gendry\">Gendry</a> catches up with them. <a href=\"/index.php/Yoren\" title=\"Yoren\">Yoren</a> refuses to hand anyone over and the gold cloaks threaten to use force, prompting Yoren's band to announce their resistance, including Kurz, who intends to use his skinning knife as weapon. In the end, the gold cloaks retreat without violence breaking out.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Avoiding the kingsroad after this encounter, the group moves west- and northwards on side roads towards the <a href=\"/index.php/Gods_Eye\" title=\"Gods Eye\">Gods Eye</a> and soon the food Yoren has brought north runs out. Yoren turns to Kurz and <a href=\"/index.php/Koss\" title=\"Koss\">Koss</a> to keep the group fed. They move ahead of the <a href=\"/index.php/Column\" title=\"Column\">column</a> and return by dusk, bringing <a href=\"/index.php/Deer\" title=\"Deer\">deer</a> or quails.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The band arrives at the eastern side of <a href=\"/index.php/Gods_Eye_river\" title=\"Gods Eye river\">the river</a> running south from the Gods Eye. While Yoren and others search a ford, Kurz catches a fish in the river with his bare hands. They move on north to <a href=\"/index.php/Gods_Eye_town\" title=\"Gods Eye town\">a town</a> on the southern shore of the Gods Eye where Yoren intends to hire boats for crossing the lake, but the town is deserted and no boats can be found. Yoren decides that they'll spend the night in the town's holdfast. He assigns Kurz, <a href=\"/index.php/Tarber\" title=\"Tarber\">Tarber</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Cutjack\" title=\"Cutjack\">Cutjack</a> the task of holding vigil from on high at the towerhouse of the town and orders Kurz to blow his hunting horn if danger threatens. Which Kurz does when men under the command of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Amory_Lorch\" title=\"Amory Lorch\">Amory Lorch</a> approach the town that night to burn it down.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Kurz is injured by an arrow when he pulls in the ladder at the towerhouse. However, he, Tarber and Cutjack survive the assault as Lorch's men cannot put the towerhouse on fire and have no patience to starve the three out. They are reunited with <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arry</a> and others who escaped via a tunnel from the holdfast, but Kurz's wound becomes infected and takes a turn for the worst. After teaching the group some much needed hunting techniques and survival skills, he succumbs to the wound and dies. Soon after his death, Tarber and Cutjack take everything of value and abandon the other survivors.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kurz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Appendix\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_5\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 5\">Chapter 5</a>, Arya II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_9\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 9\">Chapter 9</a>, Arya III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_14\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 14\">Chapter 14</a>, Arya IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_19\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 19\">Chapter 19</a>, Arya V.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405035830\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.070 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.253 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 646/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10625/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4932/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 343/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser funct